<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>New Answer Notification</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 20px auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0px 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        h1 {
            color: #333333;
        }

        p {
            color: #666666;
            font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 1.5;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 20px;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #999999;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>Hello, <%= name %>!</h1>
        <p>A new answer has been added to your question in the video "<b>
                <%= title %>
            </b>".</p>
        <p>Please Login on our platform to see the answer.</p>
        <p>Thank you for being a part of our community!</p>
